Introduction

Anlee is a South Korean singer-songwriter and producer affiliated with MYSTIC Story. He is part of the male duo ANODE. Anlee first stepped into the music scene as a solo artist, releasing his digital single “Sunrise!” on March 15, 2023.

In collaboration with Blanc, his partner in ANODE, Anlee has also contributed to the production of music for the artist Billlie.
